Anerlisa has seen the benefits of keeping her life private. The Keroche Heiress, through her Instagram, advised netizens not to expose their private lives online. "This is just a reminder that you can be on social media and not parade your private life online," she wrote. "Two years of keeping my life private has brought me peace in my life. "The likes, views and trends are not worth your peace of mind. "Truth is most of your followers pray for your downfall. You owe no one any explanation. Just do you. That all." Earlier, she had also posted some advice on how to avoid heartbreak. "I hope this time when you see the signs, you don’t ignore them,” she wrote.